{"tid":154433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗周生生試金戒指　南亞賊一戴無回頭","createTime":"2017-03-13T09:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T15:08:03.000Z","uid":60137,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98261d0fbd10ba47b551e83f70420e44ff111a37","tid":154433,"uid":60137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T09:56:50.000Z","msg":"元朗又發生南亞罪案，下午2時許，一名穿藍色恤衫、身型魁梧的南亞漢(約30歲)，進入青山公路元朗段87號周生生珠寶店，佯裝顧客挑選戒指，期間他要求試戴一隻值約11,200港元的金戒指，職員不虞有詐，取出讓他試戴，豈料他一戴上即奪門而出，向屯門方向逃去，職員見狀隨即大呼喝止及尾隨追截，惟匪徒已消失於人群中，姓胡(47歲)女職員無奈報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，在附近兜截賊人無果，現場附近一間路邊報紙檔的閉路電視，相信拍到懷疑涉案賊人逃走時的情況，據悉，賊人蓄鬍鬚，離開時戴着太陽眼鏡。警方將翻看珠寶店及附近的閉路電視，以進一步了解案發經過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170313/bkn-20170313160313291-0313_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170313%2Fbkn-20170313160313291-0313_00822_001.html&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=a5010a73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170313/bkn-20170313160313291-0313_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUST蝻亞賊快啲出黎啦，呢單野又有幾個別呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e06a4790905a86849876428b04a9920aa2809a","tid":154433,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f469bd624885f80e046574b910f1b6dda46205c2","tid":154433,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb17b475c55f0a4a66713c3b1fa3b7c445395c34","tid":154433,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:51:28.000Z","msg":"我識好多南亞人都係好人 踏踏實實打份工<img src=\"/